Text:
I miss Hawk and Cabbage.  And josh.  And I haven't seen anything from Jormis in a while.  It's so much emptier without them.  Just you, mm, and ship left from the old team.

Or they could just be on vacation.  I don't know.
Guess it time we pass the torch to you and the new crew like it was passed to us. As long as someone keeps upping these comics each week
Hell yeah! Love this series! You and the rest of the team never cease to make my Wednesday shine! Thanks a ton guys!
Speaking of Cabbage anyone gonn pick up Luther Strode? he posted the first two issues before he went MIA
MrDowntown, any chance you can put up clockworks 5? Thank you! Great quality torrent, great comic.
